        }
      },
      {
        "id": "analyze_intent",
        "type": "llm",
        "config": {
          "model": "deepseek-chat",
          "prompt": "分析以下英文文本的翻译需求：\n1. 文本类型（技术文档、文学、日常对话、商务邮件等）\n2. 语气风格（正式、随意、专业、亲切等）\n3. 特殊术语或专有名词\n4. 是否需要保留特定格式\n\n英文文本：{{steps.preprocess_text.output.cleaned_text}}\n\n请以JSON格式返回分析结果：{\"text_type\": \"\", \"tone\": \"\", \"special_terms\": [], \"preserve_format\": true/false}",
          "variables": {
            "english_text": "{{steps.preprocess_text.output.cleaned_text}}"
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "translate_llm",
        "type": "llm",
        "config": {
          "model": "deepseek-chat",
          "prompt": "请将以下英文文本翻译成地道、符合中文表达习惯的中文。\n\n翻译要求：\n1. 文本类型：{{steps.analyze_intent.output.text_type}}\n2. 语气风格：{{steps.analyze_intent.output.tone}}\n3. 特殊术语：{{steps.analyze_intent.output.special_terms}}\n4. 保留格式：{{steps.analyze_intent.output.preserve_format}}\n\n英文原文：{{steps.preprocess_text.output.cleaned_text}}\n\n请直接输出翻译后的中文文本，不要添加任何解释或标记。",
          "variables": {
            "english_text": "{{steps.preprocess_text.output.cleaned_text}}",
            "intent_analysis": "{{steps.analyze_intent.output}}"
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "format_output",
        "type": "code",
        "config": {
          "language": "python",
          "script": "def format_translation(translated_text):\n    # 确保翻译文本格式整洁\n    import re\n    text = translated_text.strip()\n    # 移除可能的多余换行\n    text = re.sub(r'\\n{3,}', '\\n\\n', text)\n    return text",
          "example_key": "format_markdown",
          "variables": {
            "input_text": "{{steps.translate_llm.output}}",
            "output_text": "{{steps.format_output.output.formatted_text}}"
